Though it is quite slower than polar coordinates, using rejection sampling is easy to understand as it does not require some statistics background.

```
class Solution {
public:
    double radius;
    double x_center;
    double y_center;

    Solution(double radius, double x_center, double y_center) {
        this->radius = radius;
        this->x_center = x_center;
        this->y_center = y_center;
